<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154070208" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;February 19&#x2013;25. 2 Nephi 6&#x2013;10,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<header>
<figure class="image no-print" id="figure1">
